Date: Fri, 22 May 2026 08:28:24 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 13/25] Trace PagePopup alt-tab

The old traces made a terrible stew,
With mouse crumbs and router goo.
We swept out the clatter,
Then traced the popup matter,
And learned this test broke y anew.
